name: Full user story test-case as generated user
description: Create new user, project, build configuration and run it as new user

steps.name: Create test user with fake user-data, generate fake project data

Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/users with data: {'username': 'expect', 'password': 'yxmzZo8PS9u', 'email': 'christophermiller@example.net', 'roles': {'role': [{'roleId': 'PROJECT_ADMIN', 'scope': 'g'}]}}, expected_status: 200
Auth user with creds: "('expect', 'yxmzZo8PS9u')" and get csrf token
Sending GET request to http://localhost:8111/authenticationTest.html?csrf with data: None, expected_status: 200
Send request to create new project

Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/projects with data: {'parentProject': {'locator': '_Root'}, 'name': 'big', 'id': 'mkj7OPxg1p0', 'copyAllAssociatedSettings': True}, expected_status: 200
Check if generated fake project ID: "mkj7OPxg1p0" equals ID from respond "mkj7OPxg1p0"
Create build conf for created project mkj7OPxg1p0

Create build configuration with data: {'id': 'nsXk2JxRONQ', 'name': 'brother', 'project': {'id': 'mkj7OPxg1p0'}, 'steps': {'name': 'boy', 'type': 'need', 'properties': {'property': [{'name': 'script.content', 'value': "echo 'Hello World!'"}, {'name': 'teamcity.step.mode', 'value': 'default'}, {'name': 'use.custom.script', 'value': 'true'}]}}}

Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/buildTypes with data: {'id': 'nsXk2JxRONQ', 'name': 'brother', 'project': {'id': 'mkj7OPxg1p0'}, 'steps': {'name': 'boy', 'type': 'need', 'properties': {'property': [{'name': 'script.content', 'value': "echo 'Hello World!'"}, {'name': 'teamcity.step.mode', 'value': 'default'}, {'name': 'use.custom.script', 'value': 'true'}]}}}, expected_status: 200
Check if created fake build conf ID: "nsXk2JxRONQ" equals ID from respond "nsXk2JxRONQ"
Test run created project build configuration with id: nsXk2JxRONQ
Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/buildQueue with data: {'buildType': {'id': 'nsXk2JxRONQ'}}, expected_status: 200
Verify that build with create fake id: "nsXk2JxRONQ" equals to build conf that was launched: "nsXk2JxRONQ"
